    "description": "If you're a passionate Assistant Store Manager with drive and ambition, Landmark Group India in Raipur is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Landmark Group India:\nLandmark Group India is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Implement promotional activities and in-store campaigns\n• Maintain high standards of store hygiene and cleanliness\n• Build relationships with regular customers to drive loyalty\n• Manage store operations to ensure smooth daily functioning\n• Train and motivate the sales team to deliver excellent service\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n• Ensure compliance with company policies and retail regulations\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Visual Merchandising\n• Proficiency in POS Systems\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n• Proficiency in Team Leadership\n• Proficiency in Retail Analytics\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Omnichannel Retail\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Raipur, Chhattisgarh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Landmark Group India!",
